About Us

Engineering Excellence Since 2014

Auto Innovate Construction (A.I.C.) is a leading industrial automation company specializing in PLC programming, safety system design, and complete automation solutions.

As a former Rockwell Automation System Integrator, we bring world-class expertise to every project. Our team has delivered hundreds of successful automation projects across Thailand, Indonesia, and India.
